Package: hydrostreamer
Type: Package
Title: A Package for Interpolating Distributed Runoff Products on to 
  Explicit River Segments
Version: 1.0.1
Author: Marko Kallio
Authors@R: c(person("Marko", "Kallio", email = "marko@markokallio.fi", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6917-7790")),
             person("Vili", "Virkki", email = "vili.virkki@aalto.fi",
                  role = c("aut"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2603-3420")))
Maintainer: Marko Kallio <marko@markokallio.fi>
Description: This package provides functions to interpolate multiple 
  distributed runoff data on to an explicitly represented river network, 
  route runoff down the network, and optimise predictions against observed 
  streamflow.
